g.tw%2Fa79132305%2F1436364100-3131919675.jpg&d=XSbuDkYM8s2eWeda%2FQGdIJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c4e6c0f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pic.pimg.tw/a79132305/1436364100-3131919675.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"af824c825bf0d82ca282a99bb2e6aa7e864dd2c8","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你就係高達？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3e429d89b0ca49066654411db62b297f4bf956","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係先死背d日文單字。每日過百個<br />\n背到n5-n2左右既單字熟曬先 <br />\n之後先去掂文法。文法n5-4最重要 <br />\n如果咩咩形果d就背曬佢。<br />\n仲有背曬單字同小小文法就可以去睇日劇（結衣）<br />\n之後慢慢上文法同補番d單字 <br />\n<br />\n利申：學左三個月。可以睇明世にも奇妙な物語。同一半有字幕日劇。</blockquote><br />\n全職讀？</blockquote><br />\n唔係喎。仲讀緊書。諗住遲小小去日本發展/讀大學</blockquote><br />\n我都有呢個打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊加油啦。我諗住依過兩三年先出發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：死窮撚。應該打工草番大約16萬先出發</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8051980dddace8f106ba73ebc52662a68cdff3","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個叫&quot;追新番&quot;既字幕組, D 日劇同動畫係繁日字幕對照, 有少少幫助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過只係動詞互換既話....一幅圖搞掂:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/a79132305/1436364100-3131919675.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fa79132305%2F1436364100-3131919675.jpg&d=XSbuDkYM8s2eWeda%2FQGdIJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c4e6c0f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic.pimg.tw/a79132305/1436364100-3131919675.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cf9f6dc79577393e50d6bb7b4eb952843bfaf9","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲係日本讀緊書又或者做野？入嚟分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b439422473edc0a98f3cc526f04844fb532390f2","tid":412343,"uid":53611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"想出去學啲進度快啲嘅班 邊度學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625f9f2408288dd11072b989d1899bc961b6b829","tid":412343,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想出去學啲進度快啲嘅班 邊度學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npasona有真日本人教<br />\n有錢既話一對一都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30f74e6e432b824f1fa623e932882617183faa7","tid":412343,"uid":136488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"kindle揾幾本有興趣既小說睇<br />\n查字典方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03b509ecc26f1feb3a911d161a5e936855298e5","tid":412343,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hea讀左一排，發覺好多野都追唔到，辞書形個啲成日唔知點樣轉法<br />\nwriting,speakimg完全唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇大神教下我點讀，好想學好日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單講<br />\n動詞轉形  自,他動詞  助詞概念 造句結構<br />\n呢D野主宰左 文章 同 句字<br />\n<br />\n你唔好諗住自己 睇完個Ch. 會記得住<br />\n我識太多人 <br />\n同我講自己 3個月記到N2 6個月聽得明N1/新聞<br />\n佢地唔係吹水,但 出來講野/寫野好似弱智咁<br />\n<br />\n知道動詞變形 同知道點用日文係 兩回事<br />\n如果你冇好環境 eg:自學/老師戇鳩<br />\n你每睇完一課  作 廿句 日文句子<br />\n<br />\n例如 動詞變形 係你個腦到 <br />\n要 學到 好似自動轉咁撚樣既境界先算過骨<br />\n因為呢D N4 基礎 你唔熟到好似本能反應咁的話<br />\n你去到後面會好撚痛苦<br />\n<br />\nTL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />R 有本野叫 <br />\n短期集中 初級 日本語文法 總まとめポイント２０<br />\n姦好佢 N3 都會過(基本上N3 只係N4既 多花式版)<br />\n<br />\n(利申: 留日中 基礎好差 <br />\n學到中間 差D放棄過既人)"},{"pid":"f0620e1eb92f1f40983065c932f3a3aba9e79a80","tid":412343,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hea讀左一排，發覺好多野都追唔到，辞書形個啲成日唔知點樣轉法<br />\nwriting,speakimg完全唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇大神教下我點讀，好想學好日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單講<br />\n動詞轉形  自,他動詞  助詞概念 造句結構<br />\n呢D野主宰左 文章 同 句字<br />\n<br />\n你唔好諗住自己 睇完個Ch. 會記得住<br />\n我識太多人 <br />\n同我講自己 3個月記到N2 6個月聽得明N1/新聞<br />\n佢地唔係吹水,但 出來講野/寫野好似弱智咁<br />\n<br />\n知道動詞變形 同知道點用日文係 兩回事<br />\n如果你冇好環境 eg:自學/老師戇鳩<br />\n你每睇完一課  作 廿句 日文句子<br />\n<br />\n例如 動詞變形 係你個腦到 <br />\n要 學到 好似自動轉咁撚樣既境界先算過骨<br />\n因為呢D N4 基礎 你唔熟到好似本能反應咁的話<br />\n你去到後面會好撚痛苦<br />\n<br />\nTL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />R 有本野叫 <br />\n短期集中 初級 日本語文法 總まとめポイント２０<br />\n姦好佢 N3 都會過(基本上N3 只係N4既 多花式版)<br />\n<br />\n(利申: 留日中 基礎好差 <br />\n學到中間 差D放棄過既人)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學左5年<br />\nn3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7e37a7ca56e563546f04ea06f39e998ad17692","tid":412343,"uid":118562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"32653361448031d877aa31a1f74792aaaa8befcf","tid":412343,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0288a358b674e35be007bbcf20bb41613aac2d63","tid":412343,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"對我嚟講睇綜藝節目效果係最好<br />\n日劇動漫雙語字幕實有幫助"},{"pid":"30260f154a6bcf198a5a01abf3452c316f827fe1","tid":412343,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"去日本讀，吸收下啲天地靈氣"},{"pid":"d3b7f3ea26c8426c83a8c12f96985c84a470eec5","tid":412343,"uid":143419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"本身對日本野有冇興趣先???<br />\n<br />\n我反而係睇好多日本綜藝 聽日文歌，從中學生字同培養語感，死背生字就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 未考過級，諗住下年考N2或N1"},{"pid":"2f4ba171546c8970cc11c3c6905197de9041863d","tid":412343,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"記住名詞文動詞文同形容詞文三種文體最基本結構<br />\n然後學助詞用法<br />\n<br />\n其實日文只要理解到助詞基本上一定識拆句子，見到幾長既句子都可以解得通<br />\n睇書睇文章既時候唔可以靠估<br />\n每一個助詞都問自己點解，助詞前面個term同個動詞有咩關係，係句子入面係咩角色<br />\n<br />\n好多人學耐左對得多見到句句子識解但到自己寫就棟左係度既100％係唔熟助詞<br />\n甚至佢地解得通都係好彩撞中<br />\n比同一句句子佢地但助詞轉少少就會炒晒車<br />\n<br />\n之後嘗試自己砌句子<br />\n寫下日記之類<br />\n好快就可以熟練<br />\n<br />\n背出面d書既文法or句子學10世都唔會學識"},{"pid":"72dd59826722839f4286af2c1fb22971a2100985","tid":412343,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"識日文既重音會好好多"},{"pid":"c53c5a7bdd681dca65c4b1570482435f5c472583","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hea讀左一排，發覺好多野都追唔到，辞書形個啲成日唔知點樣轉法<br />\nwriting,speakimg完全唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇大神教下我點讀，好想學好日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單講<br />\n動詞轉形  自,他動詞  助詞概念 造句結構<br />\n呢D野主宰左 文章 同 句字<br />\n<br />\n你唔好諗住自己 睇完個Ch. 會記得住<br />\n我識太多人 <br />\n同我講自己 3個月記到N2 6個月聽得明N1/新聞<br />\n佢地唔係吹水,但 出來講野/寫野好似弱智咁<br />\n<br />\n知道動詞變形 同知道點用日文係 兩回事<br />\n如果你冇好環境 eg:自學/老師戇鳩<br />\n你每睇完一課  作 廿句 日文句子<br />\n<br />\n例如 動詞變形 係你個腦到 <br />\n要 學到 好似自動轉咁撚樣既境界先算過骨<br />\n因為呢D N4 基礎 你唔熟到好似本能反應咁的話<br />\n你去到後面會好撚痛苦<br />\n<br />\nTL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />R 有本野叫 <br />\n短期集中 初級 日本語文法 總まとめポイント２０<br />\n姦好佢 N3 都會過(基本上N3 只係N4既 多花式版)<br />\n<br />\n(利申: 留日中 基礎好差 <br />\n學到中間 差D放棄過既人)</blockquote><br />\nOk，有冇圖望下？本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b832cd25c704defc0fcb286437f894192d2fa0","tid":412343,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本讀，吸收下啲天地靈氣</blockquote><br />\n有呢個打算，但係未有足夠資金，就係想去之前打好啲基礎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}